<item>
            <title>[SOLR-1059] Add special variables for deleting documents, skipping rows and transforms in DIH</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1059</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There is no means to delete docs in DIH.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;add two special variables &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;$deleteDocId&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;$deleteDocQuery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;if the returned row contains these fields DIH will delete docs by id or query depending on what is present&lt;/p&gt;</description>
